➜张立标（广东）：围炉感怀
http://www.sohu.com/a/420383902_100115135	43693
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/44d7e798b07647e0bf980d19539ab47f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>围炉感怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/张立标</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晴空万里暮云悠，知己相邀吟赋酬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把盏围炉熏岁月，虔心简墨品春秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生快意茶三碗，天地清欢酒一瓯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">且趁闲身犹未老，萧萧落叶悟沉浮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/68326f44441945eda5246b95b62a2502.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
