<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一片桃花开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/彩虹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当人生短路时（白纸大脑）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回一回头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好像，好像有许多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">许多事未做</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">许多话未说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一扭头</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一片桃花开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>红红艳艳，娇美如披着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>红盖头新娘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>低羞，含情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在这秋丝凉凉夜晚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这霓虹灯下</p>
